  rdfs:comment           "Supporting evidence statement (PMID:25366321): Caenorhabditis elegans has a single gene encoding RtcB, which we named rtcb-1. Caenorhabditis elegans RtcB/RTCB-1 is 73% identical to human RtcB/HSPC117 and 30% identical to E. coli RtcB (Supplementary Fig S1). " ;
